TexturedQuad.description: A simple 3D surface which displays the contents of a texture. Use with Texture constant.

ToggleButton.description: This button stays pressed after pressing it. Press again to release.

TouchpadComponent.description: Get 2D input from the player hand touching a surface.

TriggerHandle.description: Detects input when a player pulls the trigger.

TriggerVolume.description: Keeps track of players or non-decorational objects inside the volume.

WearableHandle.description: Allows you to put on items.

WelcomeMat.description: Players will spawn on a welcome mat when joining the room. You can use CV2 to send players to specific Welcome Mats when going to other rooms!

RoomDoor.description: Link to other rooms and subrooms!

Seat.description: A cushion that sits and rigidly attaches players that grab/interact with it, even if the Seat moves or rotates.

SharedGameAI.description: Shared Game AI's brain and audio location. As opposed to regular Game AI, all players in a room share the same context. Check Game AI in Room Settings for information about usage costs.

Spotlight.description: Shines light in a circle like a flashlight.

SunDirection.description: Arrow direction determines sun direction. Used with Room Sun Modify and Sun Constant Chips.

AnimationController.description: Animate objects that are wired to this controller. Edit to animate. Room level objects only.

AudioPlayer.description: Play Audio from Sample, Music SFX, or Custom Audio Constants.

AvatarItemDisplay.description: Use this to display avatar items.

Beacon.description: Beam with circuit-driven color and height.

CollisionDetectionVolume.description: A trigger volume used for detecting collisions at high speeds.

DialogueUI.description: The Dialogue UI Component is a floating text box with some optional labels, an optional directional affordance, and up to four buttons.

DomeLight.description: Creates light in a dome around the gadget.

Emitter.description: Plays a configurable, looping particle effect.

ExplosionEmitter.description: Plays a one-shot explosion particle effect.

GameAI.description: Game AI's brain and audio location. Use with the Game AI chipset. Check Game AI in Room Settings for information about usage costs.

Grabber.description: Grabs the specified object, optionally snapping it to the Grabber's position, and releases it on command. Configure for additional options.

InteractionVolume.description: Interaction Volume that supports hold interaction.

InvisibleCollision.description: Prevents players / objects from entering a region (also, you can't see it).

LeaderboardProjector.description: Displays a leaderboard for your room.

MotionTrail.description: Generates a motion trail when attached to moving objects.

Pathfinder.description: Uses a NavMesh to move around the room.

PointLight.description: Shines light in all directions like a light bulb.

Replicator.description: Dynamically spawn copies of the target object.

FullBodyCostumeDummy.description: Costume dummy with limbs. Edit a body part to add shapes!
